text: Papuapterote is a genus of moths in the family Eupterotidae.The Giant Lappet Moths (Lepidoptera: Eupterotidae) of Papua Indonesia ==Species== * Papuapterote crenulata (Joicey & Talbot, 1916) * Papuapterote punctata (Joicey & Talbot, 1916) * Papuapterote styx (Bethune-Baker, 1908) ==References== Category:Eupterotinae Category:Moth genera
title: Papuapterote
